			README for Infomercial 
		       (Brian Wilson, 5/20/94)

This is the infomercial for MAE 1.0.  You can think of it as an extremely 
primitive hypercard.  It has a scripting language.  Learn it, love it, live it.

-- brianw@apple.com
   Brian Wilson


